#5             TRUE       FALSE         FALSE      FALSE            TRUE           TRUE   51
#6             TRUE        TRUE          TRUE       TRUE            TRUE          FALSE   13
#7             TRUE        TRUE          TRUE       TRUE            TRUE           TRUE 2029
#^ the last line of the above output shows that in the trap dataset we have 2029 wild fish that have ALL of the required variables (TRUE): a GenStock, an Age, a swAge, a Brood Year, a Length, and a Sex.


